(\"failed to fetch list of istiocsr resources: %w\", err)\n508\t\t}\n509\t\n510\t\tif len(istiocsrList.Items) <= 1 {\n511\t\t\treturn nil\n512\t\t}\n513\t\n514\t\tignoreProcessing := false\n515\t\tfor _, item := range istiocsrList.Items {\n516\t\t\tif item.GetNamespace() == istiocsr.Namespace {\n517\t\t\t\tcontinue\n518\t\t\t}\n519\t\t\tif item.CreationTimestamp.Time.Before(istiocsr.CreationTimestamp.Time) ||\n520\t\t\t\t// Even when timestamps are equal will skip processing. And if this ends\n521\t\t\t\t// up in ignoring all istiocsr instances, which means user must have created\n522\t\t\t\t// all in parallel, onus is on user to delete all and recreate just one required\n523\t\t\t\t// instance of istiocsr.\n524\t\t\t\titem.CreationTimestamp.Time.Equal(istiocsr.CreationTimestamp.Time) {\n525\t\t\t\tignoreProcessing = true\n526\t\t\t}\n527\t\t}\n528\t\n529\t\tif !ignoreProcessing {\n530\t\t\t// This is the oldest instance, allow it to proceed\n531\t\t\treturn nil\n532\t\t}\n533\t\n534\t\t// This instance should be rejected as there's an older or equally old instance\n535\t\tvar condUpdateErr, annUpdateErr error\n536\t\tif istiocsr.Status.SetCondition(v1alpha1.Ready, metav1.ConditionFalse, v1alpha1.ReasonFailed, statusMessage) {\n537\t\t\tcondUpdateErr = r.updateCondition(istiocsr, nil)\n538\t\t}\n539\t\tif addProcessingRejectedAnnotation(istiocsr) {\n540\t\t\tif err := r.UpdateWithRetry(r.ctx, istiocsr); err != nil {\n541\t\t\t\tannUpdateErr = fmt.Errorf(\"failed to update reject processing annotation to %s/%s: %w\", istiocsr.GetNamespace(), istiocsr.GetName(), err)\n542\t\t\t}\n543\t\t}\n544\t\tif condUpdateErr != nil || annUpdateErr != nil {\n545\t\t\treturn utilerrors.NewAggregate([]error{condUpdateErr, annUpdateErr})\n546\t\t}\n547\t\n548\t\treturn common.NewMultipleInstanceError(errors.New(statusMessage))\n549\t}\n550\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"427a85e6-1667-473a-ac9a-f49af637134d","uuid":"231e5020-8c0e-4092-b52d-d3f90f83cba9","timestamp":"202